g.aria-label: Note: At this point, it is just asequence of characters
Convert a sequenceof characters into asingle number. Once calculated, TeX storesthat number in a variable called curcs
Use curcs to consult TeX'sbig internal "dictionary"
Use the number(integer value) curcsto find the "meaning"of the jobnamecommand.
The lookup process (consultingthe "dictionary") yields two further numbers which provideTeX with the "meaning" of the jobname command.
This is how TeX knows the meaningof what it has just processed
